 "description": "Of two sorts — woodland and meadowland. Per 50 Elves one is above normal: roll d4 for fighting level and d6 for magic level (1s count as 2s; magical 6s as 5s); per 100, a Hero/Warlock. Half a party bears bows, half spears, all carry swords. They move silently, near-invisible in gray-green cloaks; with magical weapons they add a pip to each damage die (2-7 per die). Afoot they split-move and fire; mounted they cannot, being no natural riders.",
